    "description": "Rhenus Logistics India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Supply Chain Manager at our Kolkata location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Rhenus Logistics India:\nRhenus Logistics India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kolkata, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Rhenus Logistics India!",
